CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 16, 1946, pg. 3 reads: "Acquire Degrees - ...Miss Christine Smith has received a Bachelor of Arts degree from the University of Pittsburgh. She is employed as librarian at the Homewood Library, and resides with Mr. and Mrs. Henry Jefferson. -Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Christine Smith wearing dark graduation gown with light colored collar and mortar board, posed in Harris Studio
